Study Title: Efficacy and Safety Study of NeuVax™ (Nelipepimut-S or E75) Vaccine to Prevent Breast Cancer Recurrence
Brief Summary:
Purpose of this trial:

1. To assess the efficacy and safety of NeuVax™ administered with adjuvant Leukine® (sargramostim, GM-CSF).
2. To evaluate and compare the disease free survival (DFS) in the vaccinated and control subjects.
Conditions: Breast Cancer With Low to Intermediate HER2 Expression
Interventions: BIOLOGICAL: NeuVax™ vaccine|BIOLOGICAL: Leukine® (sargramostim, GM-CSF) and water for injection
